Merda!

1163
01:37:51,824 --> 01:37:53,066
Droga!

1164
01:37:59,332 --> 01:38:01,951
Merda! Segura!

1165
01:38:02,877 --> 01:38:04,378
<i>Me puxa, Tee.</i>

1166
01:38:04,379 --> 01:38:05,780
Entendido.

1167
01:38:25,525 --> 01:38:26,691
Como está?

1168
01:38:26,692 --> 01:38:28,264
Bem.

1169
