01:42:53,209 --> 01:42:54,701
Meu Deus.

1208
01:42:57,213 --> 01:42:58,660
Walter.

1209
01:42:59,298 --> 01:43:01,450
Localização da forma de vida.

1210
01:43:02,218 --> 01:43:04,165
Algum movimento?

1211
01:43:07,181 --> 01:43:08,582
Walter!

1212
01:43:09,016 --> 01:43:10,417
<i>Aguarde.</i>

1213
01:43:13,979 --> 01:43:15,730
Ali está.

1214
01:43:15,731 --> 01:43:18,108
Convés B
entre os hexágonos 3 e 4.

1215
01:43:18,109 --> 01:43:20,011
<i>Indo pros alojamentos.</i>

1216
01:43:20,027 --> 01:43:21,903
<i>Tem alguém lá?</i>

1217
01:43:21,904 --> 01:43:23,113
Ricks e Upworth.

1218
01:43:23,114 --> 01:43:25,365
