1219
01:43:25,366 --> 01:43:27,450
Walter! Soa o alarme!

1220
01:43:27,451 --> 01:43:28,852
Avisa os dois!

1221
01:43:29,036 --> 01:43:30,453
<i>Atenção.</i>

1222
01:43:30,454 --> 01:43:32,497
<i>Ricks e Upworth,</i>

1223
01:43:32,498 --> 01:43:35,401
